Save records to EcoExtract database (internal)

save_records_to_db.Rd

Save records to EcoExtract database (internal)

Usage

save_records_to_db(
  db_path,
  document_id,
  interactions_df,
  metadata = list(),
  schema_list = NULL,
  mode = "insert"
)

Arguments

db_path

Path to database file

document_id

Document ID

interactions_df

Dataframe of records

metadata

Processing metadata

schema_list

Optional parsed JSON schema for array normalization

Value

TRUE if successful
